overview: The user wanted to elevate the visual appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, moving beyond its current generic look. The assistant
  initiated a detailed review of the app's styling, identifying areas such as
  the color palette, layout, and component designs that needed improvement. The
  approach involved implementing a new, calming sleep-themed color palette,
  enhancing the main form's layout with subtle decorative elements and a
  redesigned progress indicator, and transforming the welcome screen with a hero
  section and feature cards. Key UI components like checkboxes, radio buttons,
  and sliders were polished for better visual feedback. Additionally, section
  groupings were refined, and the report section received a more professional
  and consistent design. The outcome is a significantly improved aesthetic that
  is more aligned with a sleep health application, providing a more engaging and
  trustworthy user experience.
